definition: to be limited to/to be confined to
to set a time limit/time limit/deadline
to limit/to confine/to restrict sth within set boundaries
scope of authority/extent of power/(access etc) privileges

sentences.english: You may be genuinely helping, but only at the cellular level.
sentences.chinese: 你可能真誠地幫助，但是隻限在細胞層次。

sentences.english: Ordained Buddhist monk aged 18 – 35 of all nationalities.
sentences.chinese: 不限國籍，年齡爲18至35歲的佛教比丘。

sentences.english: The spiking test shows that the detection limit of this method is 10 oocysts.
sentences.chinese: 加標試驗表明，該方法的檢測限爲10個卵囊。

sentences.english: Runaway conditions are also predicted by tracing solution curves using continuation method.
sentences.chinese: 由連續性算法跟蹤解曲線也可獲得“飛溫”限。

sentences.english: By means of the formula, mixed-mode fatigue thresholds of the material can be calculated.
sentences.chinese: 依此式可以估算各種複合比加載條件下的疲勞門檻限。

sentences.english: Guests can also free use the brandnew hot spring baths with a appointment.
sentences.chinese: 住宿貴賓可不限次數預約無償使用全新私人風呂湯屋。

sentences.english: Other noteworthy features include unlimited storage and support for twenty languages.
sentences.chinese: 其他值得一提的特色包括不限容量及20種語言支持。

sentences.english: Their filesize limit is 100MB and each file can be downloaded unlimited times.
sentences.chinese: 文件大小限100M，無限時下載。

sentences.english: When it comes to alcohol calories, limit yourself to one.
sentences.chinese: 談到酒精中所含的卡路里，請以一杯爲限。

sentences.english: The allowance per passenger is 25 kgs.
sentences.chinese: 每個旅客的行李重量限25公斤。

sentences.english: And then, the bounds would be much easier to set up with u and v.
sentences.chinese: 於是，通過u和v的表示，積分限就更容易設立了。

sentences.english: There is no restriction on the number of participants from each organisation.
sentences.chinese: 全程約九千米，參加者年齡不限。

sentences.english: First and foremost, I have never heard about any restriction on the ROK.
sentences.chinese: 首先，我沒有聽說所謂的“限韓令”。

sentences.english: The expenses shall not exceed 200 yuan.
The coupon is not transferable or redeemable for cash.
sentences.chinese: 兌換券限本人使用，不得轉讓或兌換現金。

sentences.english: Git supports an unlimited number of parent revisions during a merge.
sentences.chinese: Git支持從不限數量的分支中進行合併操作。
